=== Pronunciation ===
*{{AHD|/drūp/}}

=== Intransitive verb ===
'''to droop'''
#to sink or hang downward; to [[sag]]
#:''I'm not handsome in the classical sense. The eyes '''droop''', the mouth is crooked, the teeth aren't straight, the voice sounds like a Mafioso pallbearer, but somehow it all works.'' &ndash; William Wordsworth
#to slowly become limp; to bend gradually
#to lose all [[enthusiasm]] or [[happiness]]

=== Noun ===
'''droop'''
#something which is [[limp]] or [[sag]]ging; a condition or [[posture]] of drooping
#:''He walked with a discouraged '''droop'''.''

